    ("en_US",  "LOC_EVENT_GOODY_ANCIENT_FORTIFICATION_EFFECT",                     "When our {1_UNITNAME} reached the village, the villagers had taken refuge in a fortification that looked quite old. The fortification looked well established and highly defensible, but the crumbling walls showed it is not flawless. Should we launch a siege, or just scavenge the supplies left behind in the village and leave?"),
